data.description: Come check out this 4 bedroom, 3 full bath home when it hits the market next week! Here are all of the updates: Kitchen cabinets, LVP and tile flooring, fixtures, outlets, front and back door, new vanities in all bathrooms plus some other updates to be completed in the coming weeks.  The other updates coming are granite counter tops in the kitchen, a new heat pump and a new concrete patio at the back dining room door. You're are going to love this home, don't miss out and get a showing scheduled ASAP.
